# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# HHT Quinceañera Cruise Invitation — environment variables
# ------------------------------------------------------------------
# This project needs NO environment variables to build or deploy.
# All invitation content (names, links, prices, contact info) lives in:
#
#   src/data/invitation.ts
#
# The interest form uses Netlify Forms, which requires no API keys.
# Email notifications for new leads are configured in the Netlify
# dashboard (see README.md → "Lead email notifications"), never here.
#
# If you ever add build-time variables, prefix them with VITE_ so Vite
# exposes them to the app, and remember anything prefixed VITE_ is
# PUBLIC (visible in the browser). Never put secrets in this project.
#
# Example (not used today):
# VITE_ANALYTICS_ID=
